theorem Topology.interiorClosureInteriorClosure_eq {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    (A : Set X) :
    interior (closure (interior (closure A))) = interior (closure A) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  ·
    have h : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A := by
      apply closure_mono
      exact interior_subset
    exact interior_mono h
  ·
    have h : interior (closure A) ⊆ interior (closure (interior (closure A))) := by
      have h_open : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
      have h_subset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) :=
        subset_closure
      exact interior_maximal h_subset h_open
    exact h

theorem Topology.P2_interiorClosure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P2 (interior (closure A)) := by
  have hOpen : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
  exact (IsOpen_P2 (A := interior (closure A)) hOpen)
